    ").• Interdisciplinarily, the keywords also manifested more collaborations between human creators and AI models.On the one hand, experts introduced principles in the diffusion process (e.g., step-aware) and concepts from artistic areas (e.g., layer-aware), to boost controllability and performance.",
    "On the other hand, researchers ventured into understanding implicit latent (e.g., disentanglement), adapting the system to user inputs (e.g., prompt), and catering the diffusion model to the human thinking process (e.g., interaction).In Sec.",
